org.chronos.chronodb.internal.api

Interface BranchInternal

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Branch
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BranchImpl

    public interface BranchInternal
extends Branch
    An extended version of the Branch interface.

    This interface and its methods are for internal use only, are subject to change and are not considered to be part of the public API. Down-casting objects to internal interfaces may cause application code to become incompatible with future releases, and is therefore strongly discouraged.

      • getTemporalKeyValueStore

        TemporalKeyValueStore getTemporalKeyValueStore()
        Returns the TemporalKeyValueStore for this branch.

        This method is not considered to be part of the public API. API users should never call this method directly, as it is intended for internal use only.

        Returns:

        Associates the given TemporalKeyValueStore with this branch.
        Parameters:
        tkvs - The temporal key value store to use in this branch. Must not be null. Must not be owned by any other branch.
